{"tid":1599681,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"印度百歲老婦被姦致死","createTime":"2019-09-28T06:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:57:16.000Z","uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7be8fabcdf0a61a6c773876889c1d4e22fdd7720","tid":1599681,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:56:15.000Z","msg":"印度婦女遭到性侵的新聞無日無之，竟然連100歲的女人瑞都不放過。在北方邦（Uttar Pradesh）30日晚間便發生了駭人的性侵案，一名100歲的老婦傷重身亡。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，被害老婦當日參加完親友婚禮回家後不久便就寢休息，未料深夜竟有一名35歲醉酒男子闖入屋內，將老婦強姦。由於案發當下發出聲響，男子被老婦家屬即場捉住，但老婦送醫後仍因傷重宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者40歲的孫子表示，祖母身體一直很虛弱，只能發出微弱的呼喊聲，所以當他們趕到現場時，才發現祖母正遭到性侵。他說，疑犯當時企圖逃跑，但被家人和鄰居聯手制服，報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n該名醉酒男子被捕後供稱，他當時因為喝了酒，想找人洩慾，在闖入村內一處住家後，發現屋內只有一名老婦熟睡，故強姦老婦。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子被控性侵及謀殺等罪名，儘管他當場就逮，但仍否認犯案，在當地引起民憤，要求將兇手處以死刑。"},{"pid":"0b220889f59a15b96923af3c33fc7e532f7c91f9","tid":1599681,"uid":259321,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqHqyQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqHqyQK.jpg&h=0796b3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線請留低你嘅DNA!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHujkN.gif&h=37db3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do9jmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do9jmF.jpg&h=efc8703c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JoOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JoOj.png&h=2d0ace40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"}]}